fulltitle: Dave Frank master class - An afternoon with Dick Hyman
description: http://www.davefrankjazz.com  Join pianist/educator Dave Frank for a unique live master class with jazz legend Dick Hyman! Includes two new great solo performances by Dick, two Dick Hyman/Dave Frank *burnin* duo piano performances, and loads of interesting, informative and educational information. For anyone interested in jazz piano, this is a historic document granting an in-depth look at into the mind and music of a jazz icon.
